title: Floor Duster + Sweeper
description:
New for 2017! Our Floor Duster + Sweeper is two in one. 
• Rotating sweeper picks up large debris
• Quick clean convenience – no dustpan needed
• Easy to empty crumb catcher
• Machine washable microfiber pad picks everything else up 
• Safe to use on all floor types
• Two piece pole for easy, compact storage
